<p>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >bananas</a>  indicates an abundance of sustenance, closeness to God, and other interpretations that we will explain for single women, pregnant women, married women, divorcees, and men, such as eating <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/أكل-الموز-في-المنام?page=945" >bananas</a>  that are yellow or green, dreaming about <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الموز-الفاسد?page=951" >rotten bananas</a> , small or large, picking bananas from the tree, or dreaming of eating banana peel for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" >Ibn Sirin</a> ,  Al-Nabulsi, Imam al-Sadiq, Ibn Shahin, Fahd al-Asimi, and many other interpretations.  You will then be informed of the following topic:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of Bananas in a Dream</span></h2>
<p>Whoever sees bananas in a dream, this has many indications, such as: <strong>Bananas in a dream indicate the presence of abundant food and kindness, and also indicate the birth of a new <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ولادة-طفل-في-المنام?page=943" >child</a>  in the family, and indicate the presence of someone close to you in distress, such as being in prison or suffering from an illness.</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >Seeing bananas</a>  in a dream indicates that there is a source of livelihood for the dreamer, but he is a person who seeks the world and its desires and does not seek the hereafter.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
