</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>As for those who dream of bananas in a dream, if he is a religious man, then this is an increase in religion and closeness to God, and if the person is a merchant, then it is money and livelihood.<br/>As for the person who dreams of a whole banana in a dream, this means that this person is righteous, sincere, and close to God Almighty.</p>
<p>Bananas in a dream also indicate the presence of love and friendship, and the dream of bananas indicates the presence of a generous and loving believer.</p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >Seeing bananas</a>  in a dream for a single woman: Seeing eating <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/أكل-الموز-في-المنام?page=945" >green bananas</a>  symbolizes positive changes in the girl's relationships.<br/>Also, seeing the sale or purchase of bananas in a dream symbolizes good and marriage, God willing.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
