</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >Seeing bananas</a>  in a dream for a married woman: The interpretation of seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >bananas</a>  symbolizes the luxurious life that the wife lives, as well as her marital and family stability.<br/>Similarly, seeing the planting of bananas and planting them in the ground symbolizes a pious son who has authority, God willing.</p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >Seeing bananas</a>  in a dream for a pregnant woman: Bananas symbolize a boy in a dream, it is a symbol of the type of the newborn, and God knows best.<br/>Bananas also symbolize ease of pregnancy, labor and delivery, God willing.<br/>It also interprets an abundance of livelihood, an abundance of money, comfort, and prosperity for the pregnant woman.</p>
<p>Bananas in a dream indicate money and indicate the fetus or indicate the presence of a person in his grave or prison, because bananas indicate clothes, intimacy, and love.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
