</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Whoever saw that he <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/أكل-الموز-في-المنام?page=945" >ate bananas</a> , money will come to him from a company or from a non-Arab, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/أكل-الموز-في-المنام?page=945" >eating bananas</a>  for the sick is not praised and is afraid of death, because of its color and name, which is close to the word "death".</p>
<p>Bananas in a dream are non-Arab in piety and dignity, they derive benefit and profit from it, and work that benefits them and everyone.</p>
<p>Perhaps bananas in a dream indicate a person who has two qualities, each of which is useful for many things, and this was deduced from its leaf because it is green or dry, and each enters into different matters.<br/>Whoever saw a banana sprout in his house and has a bunch, but it is green, this is interpreted as the birth of a son, because God Almighty said: {And a ripe fruit} and it is a banana.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
