</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>As for the hard banana in a dream, it indicates a person who sometimes takes words of bitterness and sometimes sweetness and does not remain in one state at all.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of Bananas in a Dream for a Single Woman</span></h2>
<p>The girl who sees in her dream that she is buying bananas or eating them, this is a good sign and indicates that her wedding date is approaching.<br/>If the banana is green, then it indicates a new relationship and acquaintance, and selling it in the market is like being engaged, and offering it to guests, a blessed marriage, God willing.</p>
<p>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >bananas</a>  in a dream for single women is evidence that they will find good and happiness soon.<br/>Seeing a single woman that there are guests in her house and offering them bananas indicates that she will marry a good man in the next stage and will make her very happy.<br/>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >fresh yellow bananas</a>  in a single woman's dream and eating them is evidence that she will be able to strengthen her relationship with her family and achieve her goals.<br/>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >bananas</a>  in a dream for a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-غير-المتزوجة-لابن-سيرين?page=786" >single woman</a>  means that she will achieve many aspirations.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
