</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >bananas</a>  in our dreams indicates the children that the dreamer will have in the near future.<br/>Seeing also <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >fresh yellow bananas</a>  in a dream.  Evidence that the dreamer will have knowledge, piety and success in public life.<br/>Bananas in a dream, and it was clear that they were fresh, indicate that you will get money and a lot of livelihood.<br/>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-موزة-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3554" >banana</a>  in a married woman's dream means that she will become pregnant in the next stage with a boy.<br/>Eating <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/أكل-الموز-في-المنام?page=945" >bananas</a>  in a dream.  Evidence that the dreamer will recover, and if the sick person eats rotten bananas, then this is evidence of a warning of death.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of Eating <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/أكل-الموز-في-المنام?page=945" >Bananas</a>  in a Dream for a Single Woman</span></h2>
<p>For a single woman who sees bananas in a dream, this means kindness in a new and happy romantic relationship.<br/>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموز-في-المنام?page=620" >fresh yellow and delicious bananas</a>  in a single woman's dream is evidence of kindness and new romantic relationships in her life.<br/>Eating green bananas in a single woman's dream means that she will meet new people and have a relationship...</p>
