</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>As for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الرجال-في-المنام?page=447" > seeing an ugly man </a> or the existence of an indecent body, this indicates that the person will face difficulties and crises in his practical or personal life and will fall into many failures, so he does not give up or be discouraged and continues to strive until he.  He achieves his goals and aspirations, as it has been mentioned that the appearance of a man in a dream of an unmarried woman is a good sign of a good marriage, comfortable life, and God knows best.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><strong>Men in a dream according to <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></strong></h2>
<p>The respected researcher <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> explained the interpretive differences related to the social status of the diviner, for example, <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-رجل-وسيم-في-المنام?page=3353" > seeing a handsome man </a> with a smiling face for a pregnant woman proves her feeling of security and reassurance and her distance from all pressures and disturbances.  At that time, which brings her back to good health for her and her fetus, stability, and peace in her life.</p>
<p>As for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الرجال-في-المنام?page=447" > seeing a familiar man </a> for the diviner, it is considered a good sign of the existence of shared interests between them in reality that benefit both parties materially, and if the diviner is single, this indicates love and a bond.  With this person and her entry into a new phase in her life full of peace of mind and reassurance.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
	atOptions = {
		'key' : '472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d',
		'format' : 'iframe',
