<div>
<p>The dream of the street clarifies the course of life and other interpretations, we will interpret it for the single girl, the married woman, the pregnant woman, the divorced woman, the married man, and the single young man, such as walking in the street, walking in the alley. Or a wide road or crossing the long, dead, dark, or winding road according to <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> and Imam al-Sadiq and al-Nabulsi and others on the subject:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الطريق-في-المنام?page=3206" > seeing the road </a> in a dream</span></h2>
<p>The road in a dream shows a person’s life or journey in the world, and the winding or unpaved or winding road shows a difficult life that will be controlled by problems, challenges, and hardships.  A happy life full of joy, and the end of the road in a dream is a warning of the cessation of life.  .</p>
<p><strong>The long road in a dream</strong> It indicates the dreamer’s strength in patience and endurance and can indicate longevity. If a single woman sees the long road in her dream, this is an indication that a long time will pass until she gets married, and the long paved road in a dream is better than the winding road full of potholes.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
