</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>If a person sees that he is walking on a long road, this indicates that the dreamer is striving to achieve his goals and aspirations in life, and the long road may indicate the length of the year in which many problems, effort, and work will occur, but this year will culminate in the achievement of hopes and goals, and the road may be a return to the academic year.</p>
<p><strong>The highway in a dream</strong> shows accomplishment and achieving goals quickly and if a person sees in a dream that he is driving a modern car and driving fast, this is a sign of great success, and driving on the highway shows balance and stability if driving without accidents or damage while the wide highway indicates a life full of luxury and if a person sees that he is in a car race on a highway and wins it, this indicates good luck.</p>
<p><strong>The narrow road in a dream</strong> indicates a lot of failure and the difficulty of achieving goals, and the large stones in a dream indicate enemies lurking in the dreamer, and the small stones indicate the need for money or resources that help achieve success, and the difficult narrow road can be an indication of being exposed to many problems and fears in the future.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
