</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p><strong>Walking on a narrow road</strong> The rough riding in a dream indicates the dangers surrounding a person in reality, making his work difficult, while walking on a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-دراجة-نارية-في-المنام?page=599" > motorcycle </a> on a narrow and rugged road means that the person will face challenges and overcome them.</p>
<p>Seeing <strong>a deserted road in a dream</strong> It indicates salvation from confusion and anxiety, walking on the right path, and liberation from worries and loneliness, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الطريق-في-المنام?page=3206" > seeing the road </a> deserted in a dream can indicate victories and success after a lot of suffering.</p>
<p>Whoever sees that he is walking in the middle of the forest, and the road is easy, paved, and not rugged, this indicates the great kindness of the seer towards a certain matter in his life.  A forest in the rain, indicates marriage and success in the near future.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
