</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>As for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الطريق-في-المنام?page=3206" > seeing the road </a> in the middle of the sea and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-عبور-الطريق-في-المنام?page=1453" > crossing the road </a> without difficulties, it shows the end of difficulties and pains, the end of worries and sadness, and it is good news for the beginning of a new life full of joy. , happiness, abundance of good and plentiful food.</p>
<p><strong>A dark road in a dream</strong> indicates darkness in the heart and mind, due to distraction in worldly matters, while the illuminated road indicates justice, prosperity, and abundance.</p>
<p>Thorns, holes, stones, and obstacles on the road show a lot of doubts and evil thoughts in the seer’s mind, which can lead to the destruction of his life.  Small stones show the seer’s sins and ponds show disappointment, failure, and disappointment.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
