</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Meeting someone laughing and smiling in the street indicates good luck.</p>
<p>It is interpreted as a road, path, or journey of life and life.  If the road is straight, wide, spacious, and shaded, it indicates a happy life.  As for the crippled, winding, twisted, or curved road, it indicates a life full of difficulties and shocks, and whoever sees in a dream that his road ends or is cut off, it is interpreted as a cut off in livelihood.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the road in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Seeing the road in a dream is an indication of your transition from a dwelling or house to another, and your walking on the road, if it is straight, indicates the safety and tranquility of your life.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
