</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of a long road in a dream</span></h2>
<p>The long road in a dream indicates longevity as well as patience.  The long road in a dream of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-غير-المتزوجة-لابن-سيرين?page=786" > single woman </a> symbolizes the long wait for marriage, and for single women it is a desired goal that will be achieved after years.  And the long paved road is better than the long road full of potholes and obstacles, and walking on a long road indicates perseverance and effort to achieve a goal or principle.  And the long road symbolizes a long year, that is, a year in which there is a lot of work and achievement.  Maybe it was the academic or university year</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-سيارة-سريعة-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=678" > a fast car </a> on the road in a dream</span></h2>
<p>The highway or highway in a dream shows the speed of accomplishment and achieving goals, if the dreamer is driving a modern or fast car, then the vision indicates unparalleled success, especially in the field of investment or trade.  Wide highways indicate a life of prosperity in the future, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-قيادة-السيارة-في-المنام?page=926" > driving </a> here indicates the stability and balance of the visionary, as long as the traffic is smooth and free of accidents.  And if the sleeper sees in his dream that he is excelling in a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-سباق-السيارات-في-المنام?page=3759" > car race </a> while driving on a car road, he enjoys benefits from those around him.</p>
<h2><span>A rough, narrow road, or a country road in a dream</span></h2>
<p>The rough road in a dream expresses the presence of problems in the seer’s life.  The potholes in it symbolize failure, as well as obstacles.  As for the large stones, they symbolize enemies, and the small stones or pebbles symbolize defects and the need for money and the reasons for success.  The rough road in a dream is a warning to the viewer from dangers or embarking on a work that can cause hardship.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
