</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Walking on a narrow or uneven road in a dream on foot indicates the dangers that threaten the dreamer and the annoyances that he may face at work or at home.  And walking on a narrow rugged road or a farm road on a bicycle can indicate dangerous deviations in life.  Walking on narrow rugged roads on a bicycle or a four-wheel drive can indicate the success of dealing with difficulties and overcoming all problems and troubles.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the desert road or the desert road</span></h2>
<p>The road in the desert or in the middle of it indicates escape from the maze and indicates liberation from the feeling of loneliness. The desert road in a dream can express victory and success after a long wait.</p>
