<p><span></span>The interpretation of <strong>a little girl in a dream</strong> differs from one dreamer to another depending on the details of the dream and the dreamer's feelings of denial at that time. Today, we will discuss through an Egyptian website the most important interpretations of this dream based on what the great interpreters have said.</p>
