</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>But if signs of sadness appear on the face of the little girl, this suggests that the dreamer will lose someone dear to his heart, and in return, he may lose a large sum of money. <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> explained that seeing a little girl wearing elegant clothes is evidence of success in more than one field and achieving many gains in a short period of time.</p>
<p>But if you saw the little girl wearing very bad clothes and she smelled bad, this indicates an accumulation of worries and crises in the dreamer's life, and he will not be able to achieve any of the goals he was striving to achieve. long time. This is due to the occurrence of many obstacles and obstacles.</p>
<h2><strong>The little girl in the dream for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></strong></h2>
<p>A little girl in a dream, as <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> said, is a sign that the seer will enjoy more kindness, blessings and comfort in his life. He also showed that the little girl suggests adherence to religious teachings, asceticism and a happy life.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
