</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>If the little girl is thin and her features are pale and she is wearing old and tattered clothes, this indicates that the dreamer's life is full of problems and fears, and he will receive a series of bad news that will negatively affect the seer's life. his psychological state as well.</p>
<p>But if the girl is beautiful in appearance, and she has a high degree of tenderness, this indicates the grace that will dominate the dreamer's life, and grace includes money and children. Ibn Siri also believes that the dream symbolizes the longevity of the dreamer.</p>
<p>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/رؤية-فتاة-صغيرة-في-المنام?page=706" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-فتاة-في-المنام?page=4046" > a girl </a> little </a> with very bad eyes, to the point that the owner of the vision cannot bear to look at her, indicates that many sudden things will happen in his life, which will have dire consequences and he will not be able to deal with them.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
