<h2><strong>The little girl in the dream of a single woman</strong></h2>
<p>The interpretation of the dream of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-فتاة-صغيرة-في-المنام?page=626" > a little girl </a> for a single woman is evidence that the dreamer will enjoy a calm, stable and beautiful life, and she will be able to overcome all the crises that appear from time to time, but if the girl is wearing old dirty clothes, it is an indication of facing a large number of crises.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/رؤية-فتاة-صغيرة-في-المنام?page=706" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-فتاة-في-المنام?page=4046" > Seeing a girl </a> small </a> in a dream unmarried reflects a strong desire inside her for marriage and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الحمل-والولادة-لابن-سيرين?page=1" > pregnancy and childbirth </a> , knowing that the dream brings her good tidings that she will marry soon. Another where it showed that the dreamer will achieve her goals.</p>
<p>If the little girl has bad features, this is a sign that she will hear a lot of bad news that will negatively affect her life. In <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-مرض-خطير?page=3508" > serious illness </a>.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
