<p><span></span></p>
<p>The interpretation of a dream of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-سقوط-ضرس-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=49" > a tooth falling </a> for a prisoner without pain indicates that he will soon gain his freedom, while Ibn Shaheen's opinion in interpreting this dream indicated that the dreamer had recently committed a number of actions that came. Contrary to religious teachings and social morals.</p>
