<p>If an unmarried woman sees that her molars are falling out, causing her severe pain, the dream indicates that she will meet a man of bad character who will cause her many problems in her life, and the dream also indicates that she will suffer great harm.  In her life regardless of the obstacles and hurdles she faces in her life.</p>
