<p>If a married woman sees herself pulling out her molars, this is a sign that she will leave the path of disobedience and sins and walk the righteous path that will bring her closer to the Lord of the Worlds.</p>
<h2><strong>Seeing a tooth in a dream for a pregnant woman</strong></h2>
<p>The interpretation of a dream of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-سقوط-ضرس-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=49" > a tooth falling </a> <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > a pregnant woman </a> is one of the bad signs that symbolizes the dreamer's exposure to great losses in her life, and among the interpretations mentioned by <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> that the last months of pregnancy will be difficult and mixed. A number of health problems.</p>
