<p>If a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant woman </a> sees that molars are falling into her hands, the dream indicates the type of the newborn, which is "male", knowing that he will be fair with his family.  The falling of molars in a dream of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > a pregnant woman </a> indicates that she will gain a lot of financial benefits and secure her life and the life of her children.</p>
