<p>Seeing a friend kiss in a dream means reconciliation, closeness, and other interpretations. We will explain it for single, married, <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant </a>, divorced women, and men, such as kissing my friend, or I dreamed that I kissed my ex-girlfriend, or that my close friend kissed me, according to <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> and Al-Nabulsi, and more on the subject:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of a friend's kiss in a dream</span></h2>
<p><strong>It is possible that seeing a friend kiss a friend in a dream indicates that you want to be closer to him than you are in reality. Dreaming that you are kissing a friend indicates that you want to connect with this person emotionally, and this interpretation also applies to kissing a friend in a dream.</strong></p>
<p>Dreaming of kissing a friend can be a sign from your subconscious that encourages you to think about reconciling with someone you have been estranged from, and you may feel that the reason for the separation is silly.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
	atOptions = {
		'key' : '472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d',
		'format' : 'iframe',
		'height' : 250,
		'width' : 300,
		'params' : {}
	};
	document.write('<scr' + 'ipt type="text/javascript" src="http' + (location.protocol === 'https:' ? 's' : '') + '://tinyplywood.com/472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d/invoke.js"></scr' + 'ipt>');
</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Kissing dreams don't always have romantic connotations, but can also symbolize loyalty, desire, concern, comfort, and even friendship.</p>
<p>Dreaming that you are kissing a friend means that you may need companionship and to make new friends, and this may symbolize that you need the support you will get from these friendships with friends.</p>
<p>Kissing a close friend in your dream is a sign of your love and respect for your friend. This vision is a sign that you need an intimate relationship that you don't have in real life. This dream may indicate your desire to stay with them forever, or it may simply indicate your desire to be more expressive about your friendship.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
	atOptions = {
		'key' : '472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d',
		'format' : 'iframe',
		'height' : 250,
		'width' : 300,
		'params' : {}
	};
	document.write('<scr' + 'ipt type="text/javascript" src="http' + (location.protocol === 'https:' ? 's' : '') + '://tinyplywood.com/472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d/invoke.js"></scr' + 'ipt>');
</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
